<A>__{then they hear a sound. tap tap tap. rasczak signals for quiet. tap tap tap tap. it's coming from the kitchen.}
<L>__{interior kitchen day the roughnecks}
<A>__{enter cautiously. the noise is coming from a freezer. ace stands ready to fire. johnny levers open the door, jumps back as general owen, 60, tumbles out face first.}
